data.name: About Us Content
data.value: SCManagement is a sports management platform for clubs, this was developed by Computer Engineering students from the Polytechnic Institute of Setubal. With our application, clubs can manage and track all aspects of their sport, from player and team management to financial administration and event planning. We believe that technology can make club management more efficient and easier, allowing clubs to focus on what really matters: the sport.

data.name: AboutText
data.value: Welcome to SCManagement, this is a project that was developed by Computer Engineering students from the Polytechnic Institute of Setubal. As engineering students, we understand the importance of having an efficient and easy to use sports management platform, so we created SCManagement, a sports management platform for clubs that offers a variety of features to manage teams, members, events of features to manage teams, members, events and more. With our application, clubs will have access to all important information in one place, making their administration easier. In addition, we offer an intuitive and easy-to-use interface. We focus on helping clubs achieve their goals by making club management more efficient and organized. With SCManagement, clubs can focus on what really matters: Sport Performance. You want to manage your club more easily and efficiently, then try SCManagement and see the difference we can make.

data.name: DavidAbout
data.value: I'm a software engineering student at the polytechnic institute of setúbal. I am 21 years old and I am from Portugal. I have only had professional contact in sectors different from the area I am majoring in. I'm an open-minded person and I welcome any challenge. In my personal life, I admire the values of sincerity, dedication, and kindness.

data.name: DinisAbout
data.value: Hello, I'm 22 years old, I'm a university student of Computer Engineering at the Polytechnic Institute of Setubal. I have experience in the area and I am very focused on my goals.

data.name: MatiasAbout
data.value: I started my interest in programming in high school, and today I am in my third year of a degree in Computer Engineering at the Polytechnic Institute of Setúbal.

data.name: OliveiraAbout
data.value: My name is Guilherme Oliveira, I am 20 years old, a student of Computer Engineering at the Instituto Politecnico de Setubal, and I am responsible for the graphic design of this project.

data.name: PeraltaAbout
data.value: I am a student of Computer Engineering and have been interested in programming since high school. Besides that, I also practice sports, specifically Pedestrian Orienteering and Mountain Biking, where I achieved national titles and am part of the national team representing Portugal in international competitions. Sports have made me more disciplined and organized, allowing me to better manage my time to perform well in both sports and education.
